  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You are trained to not allow anything to stand in the path of your blade. You deal double damage to constructs and treat bonuses to AC as a result of a feature, jutsu or trait as half what they normally are, and once per turn, per creature, you add your proficiency bonus to the first damage roll made against a creature benefiting from a bonus to their AC as a result of the aforementioned feature. Additionally, you gain a +1d4 bonus to d20 rolls involving Dexterity.</p>",
